{"tid":571920,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"mac pro濕水 求救","createTime":"2018-02-25T06:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T14:18:58.000Z","uid":130076,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c9876890b82472098353cb8bbd8608cef8de12f0","tid":571920,"uid":130076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:37:46.000Z","msg":"兩部mac pro濕水<br />\n<br />\n(1)<br />\n15年嗰部mac pro乾左水之後重新開機<br />\n個screen有少少閃閃下<br />\n之後立即turn off再乾<br />\n之後過左幾個鐘再開返run diagnostic test<br />\nTest results normal; no issue found<br />\n擔心之後會唔會突然壞機<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8af0399b6f5a389394d1ba059d2f440bad1a958","tid":571920,"uid":130076,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"(2)<br />\n16年mac pro嗰部基本上壯烈犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n濕到一個地步係個screen入埋水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n底版 電池更不堪入目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTotal turn down<br />\n冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家勁想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba19580b4cc27d966e2f0a318b7a6487c86466ef","tid":571920,"uid":108696,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:41:21.000Z","msg":"還返比人啦"},{"pid":"67ab1371cfdf461b9fbb2622007f7ce52848debe","tid":571920,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"拎去check check<br />\n<br />\n之前MBA濕咗少少(只係跌咗落個浴室嘅地下，當時我沖緊涼但無直接用花酒淋落去)<br />\n但因為個mon跌爆咗<br />\n所以點都要整<br />\n佢打開咗部機<br />\n原來入面真係會有水漬嫁"},{"pid":"de31ff8df87632b020a362a6e3e4d3c45c8559c5","tid":571920,"uid":57835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25